{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-source-drupal\"><a href=\"#gatsby-source-drupal\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-source-drupal</h1>\n<p>Source plugin for pulling data (including images) into Gatsby from Drupal sites.</p>\n<p>Pulls data from Drupal 8 sites with the\n<a href=\"https://www.drupal.org/project/jsonapi\">Drupal JSONAPI module</a> installed.</p>\n<p>An example site built with the headless Drupal distro\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/contentacms\">ContentaCMS</a> is at\n<a href=\"https://using-drupal.gatsbyjs.org/\">https://using-drupal.gatsbyjs.org/</a></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">apiBase</code> Option allows changing the API entry point depending on the version of\njsonapi used by your Drupal instance. The default value is <code class=\"language-text\">jsonapi</code>, which has\nbeen used since jsonapi version <code class=\"language-text\">8.x-1.0-alpha4</code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-source-drupal</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-source-drupal`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      baseUrl<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`https://live-contentacms.pantheonsite.io/`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      apiBase<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`api`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// optional, defaults to `jsonapi`</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-query\"><a href=\"#how-to-query\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to query</h2>\n<p>You can query nodes created from Drupal like the following:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"graphql\">\n      <pre class=\"language-graphql\"><code class=\"language-graphql\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  allArticle <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    edges <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      node <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        title\n        internalId\n        created<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">formatString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"DD-MMM-YYYY\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>","excerpt":"gatsby-source-drupal Source plugin for pulling data (including images) into Gatsby from Drupal sites. Pulls data from Drupal 8 sites withâ€¦","timeToRead":1,"fields":{"title":"gatsby-source-drupal"},"parent":{"__typename":"File","relativePath":"gatsby-source-drupal/README.md"}},"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-source-drupal","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","gatsby-source-plugin"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"kylemathews","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/e567aa8adbd2d49cd9990ea1ed19d4eb"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-source-drupal/","id":"dd4f93ff-86e5-5769-89db-4ebd9567c7df"}}